casebody.data:
Tuesday, February 19, 2002

MOTION DOCKET

99-570. DeRolph v. State.

Perry C.P. No. 22043. Upon consideration of the request of Master Commissioner Howard S. Bellman for an extension of time to file a final report,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the request for extension of time to file a final report be, and hereby is, granted, and the final report shall be due thirty days from the date of this entry.

Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Cook, JJ., dissent.
